name: Wildatheart
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wild at heart
des: Wild at Heart is a fun and engaging personality quiz designed to help users discover which animal best matches their personality. Through a series of five yes/no questions, the quiz assesses traits like independence, social behavior, decision-making style, and problem-solving skills. At the end of the quiz, users are matched with an animal that reflects their unique characteristics, accompanied by an audio message and a visual card featuring a description and image of the animal. This playful and interactive quiz allows users to explore their inner "wild side" in a lighthearted and enjoyable way.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
